.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: drama, action, horror, time-travel, thriller, fantasy
There are 6 different nationalities: british, dutch, indian, italian, pakistani, turkish
 1. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
 2. the italian is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the turkish##8
 6. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching drama movies##7
 8. the indian is on the left or right of the italian##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
10. the turkish is in an even position##4
11. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the british##5
12. the person watching action movies and the italian have different parity positions##9
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
14. the italian is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
15. the person watching time-travel movies is the indian##1
16. the person watching thriller movies and the pakistani have different parity positions##9
17. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |     6     |
| Job           | drama | thriller | time-travel | horror   | action | fantasy |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | british    | indian     | italian | dutch     | turkish   |

