.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-3::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: light-blue, chestnut, ivory, coral, apricot, black
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, hedgehog, mouse, snake, turtle
 1. the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the bird have the same parity positions##9
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
 4. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
 7. the person who likes apricot is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8
 9. the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the hedgehog have different parity positions##9
10. the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the bird have the same parity positions##9
11. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person who likes coral is not the owner of the bird##6
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
14. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who likes black is not the owner of the bird##6
16. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes ivory##2
17. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |     5      |   6    |
| Music-Genre   | coral  | apricot  | light-blue | chestnut     | ivory    | black |
| Pet           | snake | turtle | bird  | hedgehog | chinchilla | mouse  |

