 7. the manager is in an odd position##4
 8. the analyst is the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
10. the mechanic is on the left of the manager##1
11. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
12. the owner of the cat is not the firefighter##6
13. the accountant is somewhere between the mechanic and the firefighter##7
14. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
15. the owner of the cat and the manager have the same parity positions##9
16. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |         1          |       2       |    3    |     4      |     5      |      6      |
