.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-17::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, ritmeester, baccarat, bongani, cain
 1. the ritmeester-smoker and the person drinking cola have different parity positions##9
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 4. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
 5. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 6. the person drinking milk is not the bongani-smoker##6
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person drinking juice is not the cain-smoker##6
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
12. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
13. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
14. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
15. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
16. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
17. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
18. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |  2   |   3   |   4    |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | milk | cola  | sprite | juice  | 7up       |
| Transport   | bongani     | ritmeester | cain | vegafina   | baccarat | aristoff |

