.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-18::.
City: berlin, venice, paris, boston, miami, new-york
There are 6 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, french, indonesian, japanese, malaysian
 1. the dutch is on the right of the brazilian##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 4. the indonesian is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 6. the french is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 7. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
 8. the indonesian is the person traveling to new-york##1
 9. the french is not the person traveling to boston##6
10. the indonesian is on the left or right of the french##3
11. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the dutch##3
12. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the french##8
13. the brazilian is not the person traveling to venice##6
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
15. the french is not to the left of the japanese##8
16. the dutch and the person traveling to boston have the same parity positions##9
17. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage      | boston    | miami  | berlin | new-york    | paris   | venice    |
| Nationality   | japanese | brazilian | dutch       | indonesian | french | malaysian |

