.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-19::.
6 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, pony, mouse, chinchilla, fish
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, skiing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 2. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
 4. the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is ice-hockey have the same parity positions##9
 5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 9. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the horse##7
11. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the pony##6
12. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
13. the person who's sport is golf and the owner of the fish have different parity positions##9
14. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
15. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
16. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
17. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
18. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
19. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |  6   |
| Music-Genre   | mouse   | pony  | horse | lizard   | fish       | chinchilla |
| Sport         | skiing | cycling | basketball | surfing | ice-hockey | golf |

