.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-9-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, filmmaking, reading, traveling, woodworking
6 different games are played: monopoly, go, poker, whist, bridge, billiard
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person playing billiard and the person playing poker##2
 2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person playing monopoly and the person who's hobby is filmmaking have different parity positions##9
 7. the person playing monopoly and the person who's hobby is dancing have different parity positions##9
 8. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person playing bridge is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
10. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
11. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
12. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
14. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
15. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
17. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
18. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
19. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |    5     |     6      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | traveling | reading | dancing | drawing  | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | bridge      | whist  | monopoly   | poker  | go | billiard       |

 